{"tid":17783,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"男約砲前女友 遭女友拿直髮器燙陰莖","createTime":"2016-12-02T03:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T03:48:41.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"068db5f42848e3e9ac4c0e659b37962896cccbe9","tid":17783,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/111555_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F111555_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3bdf3cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲一名男子因背著22歲現任女友帕克(Bronwyn Parker)，去找前女友約會打砲，事跡敗露後，帕克決定懲罰男子，對他施以「燙雞刑」，拿出高溫可達攝氏200度的直髮器，燙了男子的下體，導致男子三度灼傷。該案昨日開庭審理。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，帕克堅稱，自己跟男友有約在先，如果男友做出對不起她的事，就要接受懲罰。她說她只是把燙熱的直髮器放在男友下體幾秒鐘而已，男子的下體隨後紅腫起水泡，但他因為尷尬而沒有馬上就醫，之後發現不對勁才找醫生，也使得男子需花2年的復原時間。<br />\n<br />\n法官指出，帕克的行為已經讓男友「終生恐懼」，而且恐怕會有成為「太監」的風險。法官指帕克每次懷疑男友不忠，或男友承認不忠時，就會懲罰他，包括體罰。帕克行為魯莽導致他人嚴重受傷罪名成立，被判緩刑9個月。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"b4d63b5fea1c59f0b578379ce8c96c1550d40584","tid":17783,"uid":5163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:18:29.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cb00ab74852eead312150f6c14df8446a915fc","tid":17783,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:19:07.000Z","msg":"拉直佢"},{"pid":"15d0761e8fd782d6e127d33b0c0e8db493eae661","tid":17783,"uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉直佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc874925bc7a858862a09edc2e97b3f098663ae1","tid":17783,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:22:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拉直佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158adde0781328582862cfd242f8507cf1e5da49","tid":17783,"uid":48984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:45:44.000Z","msg":"變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066337475c4731223ef9410f34910f38e52d6fa7","tid":17783,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"直髮器咁細個，點解可以夾到JJ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}